These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, apricot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
1. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food         | apricot   | raspberry |
| Sport   | rowing | lacrosse    |
| Beverage     | iced-tea  | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
House: gothic-revival, victorian
City: liverpool, new-york
1. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Game      | bridge    | monopoly    |
| House   | gothic-revival | victorian    |
| City     | liverpool  | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, bus
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, lavender
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince
1. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
2. the person who likes lavender is not the prince-smoker##6
3. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Transport      | skateboard   | bus           |
| Color           | orange | lavender |
| Cigar   | prince  | dannemann      |

 #################################

 
