The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, classical
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, emerald
1. the fan of classical is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |  2   |
| Birthday        | july | january |
| Music-Genre         | classical     | gospel |
| Color   | emerald   | light-blue  |

